---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 502
  - Title: The SOphic Hydrolith
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Trust in God
---
God gave (the Sages) this gift (of the Stone) that they might not be
hindered in their researches by poverty, or driven to flatter the rich
for the sake of gain, and thus become contemptible, and as a jest or
by-word in His sight.
